description: ExternalPower: Table recording the availability and operational state of external power sources for each cell in a radio access network at specific timestamps.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of the record), Area_Name (geographic area of the cell site), CellId (unique identifier of the cell), Id2 (duplicate of CellId), Id3 (likely an internal identifier, currently all '1'), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (version of the data format), ExternalPower.availabilityStatus (availability status of external power), ExternalPower.operationalState (operational state of external power), ExternalPower.externalPowerId (identifier of the external power source).
